des:
Control your glocusent Nightlight by using this Amazon skill with your sound to control color, brightness, alarm clock, music and more!

You'll need at least one device to support Alexa's skill controls. Just search for "hello glocusent" in the Alexa app, select hello glocusent skills and "Enable Skills." The Alexa app will come with links between your Google and glocusent.

Once your glocusen Nightlight is connected to this skill, you're ready!

let {device} color to {color} 
make {device} color to {color}
adjust {device} color to {color}
change {device} color to {color}
{stop/open} the {device} 
turn {device} to {model} mode
let {device} to {model} mode
make {device} to {model} mode
let {device} play previous
let {device} play next
let {device} turn {off/on} the music
turn down {device} to {10%/20%....} 
alexa ask glocusent turn up {device} to {10%/20%....}
